name: DynamicSignupForm
descriptionHtml:
### Endpoint to generate a dynamic JSON file in the serve with the field requested in the payload.

Request payload must contain the following fields:

studentName: BOOLEN,
phNumber: BOOLEN,
email: BOOLEN
ect... ( key: BOOLEN )

Request:

POST - https://apiqa.inquitech.in/api/v1/auth/dynamicSignupForm

raw 
  {
    "studentName": true,
    "phNumber": false
}

Response:

200 - OK 

  {"status":200,"status_type":"success","message":"successfully Created","count":1,"data":[{"studentName":{"type":"text","name":"studentName","required":true,"selected":true,"value":"name"}}]}
